@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 shadow-md rounded-lg text-base-content">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Privacy Policy is a document on websites which discloses that some or all of the ways to your website vistors about what you will do with information gathered from them, how you are gathering that information and how the information will be stored and managed.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Purpose</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>This privacy policy aims to protect the personal information of users when they access and use our game and website.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Information Collection</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>We collect personal information such as email, nickname, and password when users register an account.</li>
        <li>Login information, including email and password, is used to access the system.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Information Security and Storage</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Our website is secure and accessible, ensuring that users' personal information is protected safely.</li>
        <li>Player information such as name and cash will be displayed on the main gameplay screen.</li>
        <li>Player information will be stored in the Game Manager during gameplay.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Use of Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Users' personal information will be used to manage accounts and provide necessary functions in the game, including login and registration.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Account Permissions and Management</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Only administrators have the right to manage the permissions of other accounts on the website.</li>
        <li>Follow-up questions can only be viewed by administrators.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Code of Conduct</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Users may not use offensive or inappropriate language during question creation.</li>
        <li>Question information must be clear, accurate, and not contain inappropriate content.</li>
        <li>Answers must be displayed clearly and without confusion, with high accuracy.</li>
        <li>The correct answer must have a clear description to explain the answer.</li>
        <li>The description of the correct answer must have unmistakable evidence and be cited according to APA7 standards.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Children</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>The game is suitable for all ages and does not contain any content that could be harmful or objectionable to children.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">User Rights</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Users can register a new account with a unique email and password.</li>
        <li>Users can log in to the system using the registered email and password.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Privacy Policy in the Game</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>All players must follow the rules agreed upon at the beginning of the game.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Additional Terms</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>The game may support question resource management features for teachers to diversify question resources.</li>
        <li>Volume settings are stored on the local device.</li>
        <li>The game has cute graphics that attract players.</li>
        <li>Every movement must have an animation.</li>
        <li>The Exit button will appear in the Main menu.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Changes to the Privacy Policy</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be notified on our website.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
